# Node.js Loginapp
This is a user login and registration app using Node.js, Express, Passport and Mongoose. Using MongoDb as database.

### Version
1.1.0

### Installation
Loginapp requires [Node.js](https://nodejs.org/) v4+ to run.

### Module installation
$ npm install


### Run the application
$ node app


Modify routes folder to login based on roles
admin.js
